Class DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.kafka.core.DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type.
    V - the value type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConsumerFactory<K,V>

    public class DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConsumerFactory<K,V>
    The ConsumerFactory implementation to produce a new Consumer instance for provided Map configs and optional Deserializer keyDeserializer, valueDeserializer implementations on each ConsumerFactory.createConsumer() invocation.
    Author:
    Gary Russell, Murali Reddy, Artem Bilan
